    <item>
      <title>菲律宾将在南海岛屿上建设机场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/philippines-to-develop-airport-in-south-china-sea-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与北京的关系持续紧张之际，菲律宾正在其占领的南海岛屿上修建一座机场，并宣称对这片有争议的海域拥有主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/philippines-to-develop-airport-in-south-china-sea-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 07:11:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰计划立法允许暂停偿还外债</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ukraine-plans-law-allowing-suspension-of-foreign-debt-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰计划通过一项法律，允许政府暂停偿还外债，因为该国与其国际债权人就超过 200 亿美元的债券重组条款存在争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ukraine-plans-law-allowing-suspension-of-foreign-debt-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 07:05:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团计划在经济复苏缓慢的情况下削减更多钻石产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/anglo-plans-to-cut-more-diamond-output-amid-slow-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于钻石行业持续面临需求疲软和库存过剩的困境，英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 正考虑进一步削减钻石产量，而其铂金部门的利润则进一步下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/anglo-plans-to-cut-more-diamond-output-amid-slow-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 06:26:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
